{
  "stem": "25591.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was a quasi-military operation, and I was-- I was inducted into a forced labor battalion.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was taken up north of Budapest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Danube makes a 90 degree turn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We call it the Danube bend.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There are important railroad bridges there and so on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was there, working on the railroad--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--repairing the damage.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was-- I was in the sixth of the eighth-- eight grades of the high school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But obviously, that all came to a screeching halt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I was pushed into this forced labor camp along with everybody else.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that was the second phase.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And while quite a few of my colleagues were killed as a result of-- of aerial bombardment, I was-- I also worked on a-- on a-- on a heavy industrial island near Budapest called Csepel.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I worked there as a forced labor battalion person.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Between the March 19, 1944 and October 15, 1994, Hungary basically still had a non-bloodthirsty leader in the person of Admiral Horthy, who was anti-Semitic but not in a bloodthirsty fashion.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "On October 15, 1944, when the Germans got wind that he is attempting to make a separate peace with the Allies, they arrested him.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They arrested his son.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They-- they-- they organized a-- a coup.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the most vicious Hungarian fascist, the head of the Arrow Cross party, Szalasi took over.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And at that point, Jews became even more endangered.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my own personal involvement, and I don't attach much importance to-- to what happened to me personally.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Quite frankly, I didn't expect to survive after awhile.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
